    <item>
      <title>Iberdrola 寻求在西班牙合资企业中持有 AI 数据中心股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/iberdrola-seeks-ai-data-center-stake-in-spain-joint-venture</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Iberdrola SA 计划为西班牙的一个数据中心提供电网连接和可再生能源，以换取高达 20% 的设施，该数据中心的建设成本将高达 20 亿欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/iberdrola-seeks-ai-data-center-stake-in-spain-joint-venture</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 因抗议美国禁令而受到法庭严厉质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从上诉法院小组的质询来看，如果中国所有者不出售这款广受欢迎的社交媒体应用，TikTok 将面临一场艰难的战斗，以避开美国的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
